+--------------------------+---------------------+
| Microdot-II 1.3 Released | Goto: www.vapor.com |
^--------------------------^---------------------^
Vaporware has  released the new  version of Micro-
dot-II. Version 1.3 has a main focus of keeping
your messages intact upon a system crash.

+--------------+---------------------------------+
| TVPaint Docs | Goto: www.nwamiga.org           |
^--------------^---------------------------------^
You might not know, but the wonderful TVPaint 3
was released earlier for free on the Newtek web-
site. Now the NW Amiga group is trying to get
the rights to reproduce the documentation for the
program in both HTML and Printed format.

+---------------+--------------------------------+
| VVA, VNC, Etc | Goto: perso.cybercable.fr/     |
|               | dspach/sub-amiga/vva-vnc/      |
|               | vva-vnc.html                   |
^---------------^--------------------------------^
VVA is a new program which allows VNC on an Amiga.
VNC is something which allows the control of
another computer and contains the ability to see
it's screen aswell.

