+-----------------+------------------------------+
| The PC Is Dead! | Goto: www.news.com/news/     |
|                 | item/0,4,34236,00.htm?ow     |
^-----------------^------------------------------^
Yes, we're not making this up. IBM have recently
said that the PC is dead! They're now saying that
the future will be information appliance type
machines. Which is just what Jim Collas has said
the new Amiga's will be. Hmm.

